### FIND-066 (major, structural_integrity → 1a): RESOLVED
- types.ts: added DtoBlock type; added optional `blocks?: ReadonlyArray<DtoBlock>` to
  all non-idle EditingSessionStateDto arms; added required `blocks: ReadonlyArray<DtoBlock>`
  to EditorViewState.
- editorReducer.ts: mirrorSnapshot() accepts currentBlocks parameter; mirrors
  snapshot.blocks when present, preserves currentBlocks when absent; idle arm returns [].
  DomainSnapshotReceived passes state.blocks as currentBlocks.
- EditorPanel.svelte: replaced local `blocks: Block[]` with `const blocks = $derived(viewState.blocks)`.
  Initial viewState seeded with initialBlocks. Legacy fallback in handleSnapshot creates
  a synthetic block when focusedBlockId is not in viewState.blocks (test-mode compatibility).

### FIND-068 (minor, spec_fidelity → 2c): RESOLVED
- types.ts: removed IDLE_SAVE_DEBOUNCE_MS export (comment retained as migration note).
